data.description: This one won't last long!  Paved road frontage! This is a lovely 3/2 DWMH that has been updated and centrally located to the river, gulf and town. Located in the heart of Dixie. This home sits on two lots with beautiful green grass, landscaping and some fruit trees. New A/C unit in 2019, new paint, new flooring, Dog pen with 2 kennels and lots of other extras. All this sits on 1.48 acres. Only a short drive to the coastal town of Suwannee for all your salt water fishing.  Close to schools, shopping and restaurants. Bring the family and pets because there is plenty of room for everyone. Great location. Call today for details!
